<h4><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Arvo,serif"><span style="color:#666666">Present analysis</span></span></span></h4>
<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Arvo,serif"><span style="color:#000000">Issue more of quick justice delivery than nature of punishment. Public fervent for death a lot</span></span></span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type:disc"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Arvo,serif"><span style="color:#000000">NCRB says 2004-13, 1300 death penalty only 4 have been executed. "To err is human to forgive is divine".</span></span></span></li>
<li style="list-style-type:disc"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Arvo,serif"><span style="color:#000000">Many of those on death row are hardened suicidal terrorists, for whom death row will not work as a deterrent</span></span></span></li>
<li style="list-style-type:disc"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Arvo,serif"><span style="color:#000000">Death penalty for rape can lead to murder along with rape to silence the witness as noted by Fali Nariman. Justice verma also said don't give death penalty.</span></span></span></li></ul>
