<h4><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Arvo,serif"><span style="color:#666666">For argument&nbsp;</span></span></span></h4>
<ol>
<li style="list-style-type:decimal"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Arvo,serif"><span style="color:#000000">that heinous crime lifetime prisoners burden taxpayer money.</span></span></span></li>
<li style="list-style-type:decimal"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Arvo,serif"><span style="color:#000000">that keeping them alive is also a national security threat. E.g: Hijacking of IC 814 in 1999 that has led to most wanted Masood Azhar.</span></span></span></li>
<li style="list-style-type:decimal"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Arvo,serif"><span style="color:#000000">satisfaction of conscience and feeling of justice being done</span></span></span></li>
<li style="list-style-type:decimal"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Arvo,serif"><span style="color:#000000">during the great administrator Chanakya's time death penalty was a deterrent</span></span></span></li>
<li style="list-style-type:decimal"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Arvo,serif"><span style="color:#000000">with review petition, appeals and Governor/President's commutation it has enough safeguarding from miscarriage of justice.</span></span></span></li></ol>
